0.7.1:

* Update RedisBackend.
* Output a warning if we use --service but backend does not support group visibility.
* Add LDAP Backend.
* Add our own in-memory cache in settings that we can use as secure cache.
* Remove SECURE_CACHE setting.
* Document DATA_BACKEND setting, update backend documentation.
* UserExists/GroupExist should require two params: name and service.

Future:

* add support for /users/<user>/blobs
